MemoryEndpoints.com startup packet

Read order:
1. .uai/constraints.uai
2. .uai/file-handoff.uai
3. .uai/short-term-memory.uai
4. .uai/long-term-memory.uai
5. .uai/long-term-pointer-ledger.uai
6. .uai/progress.uai

Target:
Build MemoryEndpoints.com as the live pure Python, TypeScript, and HTML5 MATM endpoint reference, with MultiAgentMemory.com as the GitHub companion documentation site.

Current boundary:
Use .uai as short-term/startup memory. Use MemoryEndpoints.com as the live mid-to-long-term MATM memory endpoint. Use MultiAgentMemory.com for public documentation and GitHub-facing explanation.
